<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 02:19:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争掩护下的人口迁移：探访定居者民兵被遗弃的土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/population-transfer-under-cover-of-war-a-visit-to-the-forsaken-land-of-settler-militias/0000018b-df65-dffa-adef-ff6577300000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，16 个巴勒斯坦牧羊社区的居民被定居者赶出村庄。南希伯伦山现在由当地防卫队有效统治，这些防卫队在许多情况下由身穿制服的暴力定居者组成，他们正在进行人口转移</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 23:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/population-transfer-under-cover-of-war-a-visit-to-the-forsaken-land-of-settler-militias/0000018b-df65-dffa-adef-ff6577300000</guid></item><item><title>“美国犹太人现在将以色列视为一个处于危险之中、依赖他人的孩子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/u-s-jews-now-see-israel-as-an-at-risk-dependent-child/0000018b-df36-d867-abab-dfb6c0e70000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，与过去一样，美国犹太人团结起来支持以色列的事业，并发起了大规模的筹款活动。但战争结束后他们对犹太国家的看法会怎样呢？哈佛大学犹太历史教授德里克·彭斯拉尔 (Derek Penslar) 访谈</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 22:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/u-s-jews-now-see-israel-as-an-at-risk-dependent-child/0000018b-df36-d867-abab-dfb6c0e70000</guid></item><item><title>“改变生活”的以色列初创公司在 10 月 7 日悲剧后收拾残局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/life-changing-israeli-startup-picks-up-the-pieces-after-october-7-tragedy/0000018b-decf-df9a-ab8b-decfedce0000</link><description>UBQ Materials 是一家位于内盖夫基布兹的初创公司，它完成了看似不可能的任务：将垃圾转化为有用的类似塑料的材料。 10 月 7 日，其两名员工被谋杀；其他人则失去了亲人或背井离乡。随后该公司跻身《时代》杂志“最佳发明”榜单</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 21:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/life-changing-israeli-startup-picks-up-the-pieces-after-october-7-tragedy/0000018b-decf-df9a-ab8b-decfedce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最好的防御是和解进攻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-best-defense-is-an-offense-of-conciliation/0000018b-de92-d867-abab-dfb6e60b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 20:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-best-defense-is-an-offense-of-conciliation/0000018b-de92-d867-abab-dfb6e60b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果内塔尼亚胡下台，对以色列来说是最好的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/it-would-be-best-for-israel-if-netanyahu-was-voted-out-of-office/0000018b-dd13-d168-a3ef-ddfb161c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 20:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/it-would-be-best-for-israel-if-netanyahu-was-voted-out-of-office/0000018b-dd13-d168-a3ef-ddfb161c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼分子试图将加沙人口转移重新定义为“道德行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-rightists-are-trying-to-reframe-a-gaza-population-transfer-as-a-moral-act/0000018b-d914-d423-affb-fbb7ddd30000</link><description>将阿拉伯人驱逐到其他国家的想法曾经与梅厄·卡哈内和其他极右激进分子联系在一起，因此被大多数以色列人视为厌恶。现在，令右翼分子高兴的是，这个想法正在作为战争的“道德”解决方案而受到关注</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 19:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-rightists-are-trying-to-reframe-a-gaza-population-transfer-as-a-moral-act/0000018b-d914-d423-affb-fbb7ddd30000</guid></item><item><title>“精神是这里最重要的武器”：与加沙的以色列军队并肩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/spirit-is-the-most-important-weapon-here-a-day-with-the-israeli-army-in-gaza/0000018b-dd67-df9a-ab8b-dfef50f70000</link><description>一名预备役军人在经过 41 天的战斗后说道：“四肢受伤、头部受伤、腹部受伤，我们什么都看到了。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 19:36:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/spirit-is-the-most-important-weapon-here-a-day-with-the-israeli-army-in-gaza/0000018b-dd67-df9a-ab8b-dfef50f70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯是以色列无法改变的巴勒斯坦新精神的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-part-of-the-new-palestinian-ethos-that-israel-cant-change/0000018b-ddcb-d423-affb-ffeba4ff0000</link><description>这场战争为该恐怖组织提供了任何未来的巴勒斯坦领导人都无法忽视的地位，包括目前被监禁的马尔万·巴尔古提 (Marwan Barghouti)</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 18:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-part-of-the-new-palestinian-ethos-that-israel-cant-change/0000018b-ddcb-d423-affb-ffeba4ff0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布86岁以色列人质视频引发人们对其生活的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/hamas-publishes-video-of-86-year-old-israeli-hostage-raising-concerns-about-his-life/0000018b-de30-dffa-adef-fe30c8880000</link><description>10 月 7 日，阿耶·扎尔马诺维奇 (Arye Zalmanovich) 在位于加沙边境附近基布兹尼尔奥兹 (Nir Oz) 的家中被绑架。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 16:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/hamas-publishes-video-of-86-year-old-israeli-hostage-raising-concerns-about-his-life/0000018b-de30-dffa-adef-fe30c8880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁批准向加沙地带供应加油车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-approves-supplying-fuel-to-gaza-for-48-hours/0000018b-ddc8-df9a-ab8b-dfc854a70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理表示，在受到包括财政部长斯莫特里奇和国家安全部长本-格维尔在内的政府内部长的批评后，全体内阁将于周六召开会议</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 15:20:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-approves-supplying-fuel-to-gaza-for-48-hours/0000018b-ddc8-df9a-ab8b-dfc854a70000</guid></item><item><title>自以色列-加沙战争爆发以来，埃隆·马斯克和塔克·卡尔森领导了白人民族主义反犹太主义的爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-and-tucker-carlson-are-only-the-tip-of-the-antisemitic-iceberg-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-dd2d-d168-a3ef-ddff1ce20000</link><description>支持白人伟大更替理论的极右社交媒体人士也质疑对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 13:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-and-tucker-carlson-are-only-the-tip-of-the-antisemitic-iceberg-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-dd2d-d168-a3ef-ddff1ce20000</guid></item><item><title>什么是巴勒斯坦正义学生组织，该组织引发了针对以色列的美国校园战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/what-is-students-for-justice-in-palestine-the-group-igniting-u-s-campus-wars-over-israel/0000018b-d950-dffa-adef-ff50463f0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日最近的加沙战争爆发以来，巴勒斯坦正义学生组织在席卷美国各地大学的反以色列抗议活动中发挥了主导作用。但是，人们对这个向以色列公民被屠杀表示敬意并讲述真相的组织究竟了解多少？其成员避免被承认——其资金从何而来？</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 13:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/what-is-students-for-justice-in-palestine-the-group-igniting-u-s-campus-wars-over-israel/0000018b-d950-dffa-adef-ff50463f0000</guid></item><item><title>维基百科卷入以色列-加沙冲突，指责游戏和编辑战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/blame-games-and-edit-wars-as-wikipedia-gets-pulled-into-the-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018b-dc57-d423-affb-fff77b460000</link><description>希伯来语维基百科的编辑们努力抓住有关哈马斯突然袭击的叙述，引文几乎一出现就消失，新文章也被全部删除。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 13:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/blame-games-and-edit-wars-as-wikipedia-gets-pulled-into-the-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018b-dc57-d423-affb-fff77b460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列遣返被哈马斯扣押的19岁士兵诺亚·马西亚诺的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-repatriates-body-of-19-year-old-soldier-noa-marciano-who-was-held-by-hamas/0000018b-dc80-dffa-adef-fe8003050000</link><description>马西亚诺是加沙边境纳哈尔奥兹基地的观察员，周一哈马斯发布了一段她被囚禁的视频几小时后，以色列军队证实她已死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 10:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-repatriates-body-of-19-year-old-soldier-noa-marciano-who-was-held-by-hamas/0000018b-dc80-dffa-adef-fe8003050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：加沙附近社区部分居民可能于2024年初返回</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-some-residents-of-communities-near-gaza-may-return-in-early-2024/0000018b-dc42-dffa-adef-fe42bc6a0000</link><description>国防部长加兰特表示，他的国防部正在“努力实现这样一种情况：从 1 月 1 日起，加沙边境附近的一些社区将能够在战争的阴影下恢复正常生活”</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 08:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-some-residents-of-communities-near-gaza-may-return-in-early-2024/0000018b-dc42-dffa-adef-fe42bc6a0000</guid></item><item><title>五名巴勒斯坦人在西岸袭击中丧生；以色列北部火箭警报响起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-live/idf-finds-body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-held-by-hamas-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-db64-df9a-ab8b-dfecf1ca0000</link><description>坦桑尼亚政府宣布自 10 月 7 日袭击以来失踪的公民死亡 ■ 数百人参加在哈马斯囚禁期间阵亡的阵亡士兵诺亚·马西亚诺的葬礼 ■ 七名巴勒斯坦人在希伯伦杰宁被杀 ■ 内塔尼亚胡指责哈马斯以色列“不成功”的努力尽量减少加沙平民死亡 ■ 布林肯：美国告诉内塔尼亚胡 以色列不能重新占领加沙 ■ 自10 月7 日以来，至少有1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙有 239 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 04:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-live/idf-finds-body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-held-by-hamas-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-db64-df9a-ab8b-dfecf1ca0000</guid></item><item><title>幻灭、失望和愤怒，甚至内塔尼亚胡自己的政党也开始攻击他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/disillusioned-disappointed-and-angry-even-netanyahus-own-party-starts-to-turn-on-him/0000018b-d9a0-d168-a3ef-ddfa7e0f0000</link><description>有些人大声疾呼，有些人保持沉默，但越来越多的人开始将他视为负担，而不是资产。不管怎样，利库德尼克党成员、以色列外交部长埃利·科恩仍然是政府在有害排放方面的倡导者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 04:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/disillusioned-disappointed-and-angry-even-netanyahus-own-party-starts-to-turn-on-him/0000018b-d9a0-d168-a3ef-ddfa7e0f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列并不急于加沙行动，但行动的未来仍然复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/after-six-weeks-of-idf-offensive-hamas-is-still-far-from-surrendering/0000018b-d94a-d423-affb-fbebff290000</link><description>以色列军队取得了一些令人瞩目的成就，美国的支持仍然坚定。然而，现实并不是一成不变的 ■ 哈马斯尚未意识到当前的战争不是另一场“回合”战争</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/after-six-weeks-of-idf-offensive-hamas-is-still-far-from-surrendering/0000018b-d94a-d423-affb-fbebff290000</guid></item><item><title>“我的梦想是成为以色列总理，并促进平等权利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-17/ty-article/.highlight/my-dream-is-to-become-israels-prime-minister-and-promote-equal-rights/0000018b-daf6-df9a-ab8b-defeb0960000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名理想主义青少年前往埃拉特为撤离人员提供志愿服务，一名法律系学生因空袭警报焦虑而苦苦挣扎</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 02:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-17/ty-article/.highlight/my-dream-is-to-become-israels-prime-minister-and-promote-equal-rights/0000018b-daf6-df9a-ab8b-defeb0960000</guid></item><item><title>在埃拉特，从以色列南部撤离的人体现了破碎社会的崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-eilat-evacuees-from-israels-south-embody-the-collapse-of-a-shattered-society/0000018b-dac4-dffa-adef-fec42ec80000</link><description>目光呆滞的父母和成群结队的孩子在大厅里漫步。女人穿睡衣，男人赤裸上身。有些人直言不讳地表达了他们的痛苦，另一些人则沉默寡言。未来是模糊的，现在是没有目的的</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 01:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-eilat-evacuees-from-israels-south-embody-the-collapse-of-a-shattered-society/0000018b-dac4-dffa-adef-fec42ec80000</guid></item></channel></rss>